
See README in parent directory (top level directory of source package)
for an explanation. A more general html page needs to be written.

To view the manpage in this directory (rather than the installed one, if
this package is installed) use:
    man ./clone_pseudo_fs.8

Syntax checking
===============
Use 'mandoc -W style clone_pseudo_fs.8 > /dev/null'

The: 'cannot parse date, using it verbatim: TH February 2019' warning
can be ignored.

